      <title>特朗普誓言削减社会保障税以吸引老年人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/trump-vows-to-cut-taxes-on-social-security-in-bid-to-woo-seniors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普承诺取消老年人社会保障税，此举将减少部分美国老年人的税费，但会进一步给尚未退休人士的福利造成压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/trump-vows-to-cut-taxes-on-social-security-in-bid-to-woo-seniors</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 01:39:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯副总裁搜索团队会见夏皮罗，而劳工团体则反对凯利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/harris-vp-team-meets-josh-shapiro-as-labor-balks-at-mark-kelly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[宾夕法尼亚州州长乔什·夏皮罗会见了卡玛拉·哈里斯的代表，而一些劳工团体对亚利桑那州参议员马克·凯利表示反对，因为这位民主党候选人寻找竞选伙伴的工作已接近尾声。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/harris-vp-team-meets-josh-shapiro-as-labor-balks-at-mark-kelly</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 00:46:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平拥抱梅洛尼表明中国需要欧洲朋友</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/xi-s-embrace-of-meloni-shows-china-has-use-for-friends-in-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[习近平主席对意大利总理的热情欢迎，尖锐地提醒欧洲领导人注意与中国合作的经济利益以及潜在的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/xi-s-embrace-of-meloni-shows-china-has-use-for-friends-in-europe</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台积电激发台湾民众对中国的爱国精神</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/tsmc-sparks-patriotic-spirit-of-taiwan-investors-wary-of-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[庄周认为，她个人能做的最好的事情就是购买台湾半导体制造公司的股票，以保护她的祖国免受中国的侵略。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/tsmc-sparks-patriotic-spirit-of-taiwan-investors-wary-of-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾金融监督管理委员会提醒银行家提高警惕，中国警告“分裂分子”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/taiwan-fsc-tells-bankers-to-beware-as-china-warns-separatists</link>
      <description><![CDATA[继北京方面决定扩大对岛内“分裂分子”判处死刑的法律范围后，台湾的金融监管机构警告在大陆运营的台湾银行员工要谨言慎行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/taiwan-fsc-tells-bankers-to-beware-as-china-warns-separatists</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡马拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 任命财政部高级官员参与反对特朗普的竞选活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/kamala-harris-campaign-against-trump-hires-top-treasury-official</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 已聘请财政部官员布莱恩·尼尔森 (Brian Nelson) 为她的竞选团队效力，这是自总统乔·拜登 (Joe Biden) 决定退出后接手竞选团队以来首次增加重要工作人员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/kamala-harris-campaign-against-trump-hires-top-treasury-official</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 21:37:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马杜罗称其对手和抗议者应被判入狱 30 年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/venezuela-s-maduro-machado-gonzalez-should-be-jailed-30-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗表示，走上街头抗议的反对派对手及其支持者应被判处至少 30 年监禁，并要求该国政府控制的最高法院核实其自行宣布的选举胜利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/venezuela-s-maduro-machado-gonzalez-should-be-jailed-30-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 21:34:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马杜罗请求委内瑞拉法院核实其胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/maduro-asks-friendly-venezuela-court-to-verify-his-election-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管反对派声称有证据证明总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗窃取了选票，但总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗仍要求委内瑞拉最高法院审计周日总统选举的结果，以证明其自我宣布的胜利合法化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/maduro-asks-friendly-venezuela-court-to-verify-his-election-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 18:36:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在 NABJ 活动上质疑哈里斯对黑人身份的认同</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/trump-questions-harris--embrace-of-black-identity-at-nabj-event</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党候选人唐纳德·特朗普在与黑人记者举行的激烈圆桌会议上质疑副总统卡玛拉·哈里斯的种族身份，笨拙地试图接触有色人种选民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/trump-questions-harris--embrace-of-black-identity-at-nabj-event</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 18:26:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>缅甸军政府延长紧急状态，内战愈演愈烈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/myanmar-junta-extends-emergency-rule-again-as-civil-war-rages-on</link>
      <description><![CDATA[缅甸军政权延长了自 2021 年政变以来实施的紧急状态，因为将军们正努力平息与少数民族武装团体和民主战士的内战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/myanmar-junta-extends-emergency-rule-again-as-civil-war-rages-on</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 08:49:57 GMT</pubDate>
